001package org.jfree.chart.plot;
002
003
004import java.awt.Paint;
005import java.awt.Stroke;
006import org.jfree.chart.internal.Args;
007import java.io.Serializable;
008
009public class FastScatterPlotProduct implements Serializable, Cloneable {
010        private transient Paint paint;
011        private boolean domainGridlinesVisible;
012        private transient Stroke domainGridlineStroke;
013        private transient Paint domainGridlinePaint;
014        private boolean rangeGridlinesVisible;
015        private transient Stroke rangeGridlineStroke;
016        private transient Paint rangeGridlinePaint;
017
018        public Paint getPaint() {
019                return paint;
020        }
021
022        public void setPaint2(Paint paint) {
023                this.paint = paint;
024        }
025
026        public boolean getDomainGridlinesVisible() {
027                return domainGridlinesVisible;
028        }
029
030        public void setDomainGridlinesVisible2(boolean domainGridlinesVisible) {
031                this.domainGridlinesVisible = domainGridlinesVisible;
032        }
033
034        public Stroke getDomainGridlineStroke() {
035                return domainGridlineStroke;
036        }
037
038        public void setDomainGridlineStroke2(Stroke domainGridlineStroke) {
039                this.domainGridlineStroke = domainGridlineStroke;
040        }
041
042        public Paint getDomainGridlinePaint() {
043                return domainGridlinePaint;
044        }
045
046        public void setDomainGridlinePaint2(Paint domainGridlinePaint) {
047                this.domainGridlinePaint = domainGridlinePaint;
048        }
049
050        public boolean getRangeGridlinesVisible() {
051                return rangeGridlinesVisible;
052        }
053
054        public void setRangeGridlinesVisible2(boolean rangeGridlinesVisible) {
055                this.rangeGridlinesVisible = rangeGridlinesVisible;
056        }
057
058        public Stroke getRangeGridlineStroke() {
059                return rangeGridlineStroke;
060        }
061
062        public void setRangeGridlineStroke2(Stroke rangeGridlineStroke) {
063                this.rangeGridlineStroke = rangeGridlineStroke;
064        }
065
066        public Paint getRangeGridlinePaint() {
067                return rangeGridlinePaint;
068        }
069
070        public void setRangeGridlinePaint2(Paint rangeGridlinePaint) {
071                this.rangeGridlinePaint = rangeGridlinePaint;
072        }
073
074        /**
075        * Sets the color for the data points and sends a  {@link PlotChangeEvent} to all registered listeners.
076        * @param paint   the paint ( {@code  null}  not permitted).
077        * @see #getPaint()
078        */
079        public void setPaint(Paint paint, FastScatterPlot fastScatterPlot) {
080                Args.nullNotPermitted(paint, "paint");
081                this.paint = paint;
082                fastScatterPlot.fireChangeEvent();
083        }
084
085        /**
086        * Sets the stroke for the grid lines plotted against the domain axis and sends a  {@link PlotChangeEvent}  to all registered listeners.
087        * @param stroke   the stroke ( {@code  null}  not permitted).
088        * @see #getDomainGridlineStroke()
089        */
090        public void setDomainGridlineStroke(Stroke stroke, FastScatterPlot fastScatterPlot) {
091                Args.nullNotPermitted(stroke, "stroke");
092                this.domainGridlineStroke = stroke;
093                fastScatterPlot.fireChangeEvent();
094        }
095
096        /**
097        * Sets the paint for the grid lines plotted against the domain axis and sends a  {@link PlotChangeEvent}  to all registered listeners.
098        * @param paint   the paint ( {@code  null}  not permitted).
099        * @see #getDomainGridlinePaint()
100        */
101        public void setDomainGridlinePaint(Paint paint, FastScatterPlot fastScatterPlot) {
102                Args.nullNotPermitted(paint, "paint");
103                this.domainGridlinePaint = paint;
104                fastScatterPlot.fireChangeEvent();
105        }
106
107        /**
108        * Sets the stroke for the grid lines plotted against the range axis and sends a  {@link PlotChangeEvent}  to all registered listeners.
109        * @param stroke   the stroke ( {@code  null}  permitted).
110        * @see #getRangeGridlineStroke()
111        */
112        public void setRangeGridlineStroke(Stroke stroke, FastScatterPlot fastScatterPlot) {
113                Args.nullNotPermitted(stroke, "stroke");
114                this.rangeGridlineStroke = stroke;
115                fastScatterPlot.fireChangeEvent();
116        }
117
118        /**
119        * Sets the paint for the grid lines plotted against the range axis and sends a  {@link PlotChangeEvent}  to all registered listeners.
120        * @param paint   the paint ( {@code  null}  not permitted).
121        * @see #getRangeGridlinePaint()
122        */
123        public void setRangeGridlinePaint(Paint paint, FastScatterPlot fastScatterPlot) {
124                Args.nullNotPermitted(paint, "paint");
125                this.rangeGridlinePaint = paint;
126                fastScatterPlot.fireChangeEvent();
127        }
128
129        /**
130        * Sets the flag that controls whether or not the domain grid-lines are visible.  If the flag value is changed, a  {@link PlotChangeEvent}  is sent to all registered listeners.
131        * @param visible   the new value of the flag.
132        * @see #getDomainGridlinePaint()
133        */
134        public void setDomainGridlinesVisible(boolean visible, FastScatterPlot fastScatterPlot) {
135                if (this.domainGridlinesVisible != visible) {
136                        this.domainGridlinesVisible = visible;
137                        fastScatterPlot.fireChangeEvent();
138                }
139        }
140
141        /**
142        * Sets the flag that controls whether or not the range axis grid lines are visible.  If the flag value is changed, a  {@link PlotChangeEvent}  is sent to all registered listeners.
143        * @param visible   the new value of the flag.
144        * @see #isRangeGridlinesVisible()
145        */
146        public void setRangeGridlinesVisible(boolean visible, FastScatterPlot fastScatterPlot) {
147                if (this.rangeGridlinesVisible != visible) {
148                        this.rangeGridlinesVisible = visible;
149                        fastScatterPlot.fireChangeEvent();
150                }
151        }
152
153        public Object clone() throws CloneNotSupportedException {
154                return (FastScatterPlotProduct) super.clone();
155        }
156}
